02:10:42,760 --> 02:10:50,360
do their thing, and then they fly, first of all, to Thailand, and then they fly into LA.

1026
02:10:51,160 --> 02:10:59,480
And so how can they do anything? You know, they're in a country they don't understand.

1027
02:10:59,480 --> 02:11:06,120
They don't speak English. You know, their mission is to go train as pilots, but they would not

