1031
02:11:34,040 --> 02:11:40,520
talking to the Minister of Religious Affairs. That's kind of significant because, you know,

1032
02:11:41,000 --> 02:11:48,600
they are the, as a result of the Mecca catastrophe, Saudi put, Saudis put

1033
02:11:49,720 --> 02:11:54,440
these imams and consulates all over the place, and they had a lot of authority. So anyway,

1034
02:11:55,080 --> 02:12:01,640
Omar Bayoumi leaves the Saudi consulate, and he goes to a Middle Eastern restaurant,

1035
02:12:01,640 --> 02:12:07,960
where he happens to overhear these two guys speaking in a Saudi accent. It's, according to him,

1036
02:12:07,960 --> 02:12:14,680
and the Saudi government, a total coincidence. Do you believe that? No, not at all. No, I think,

1037
02:12:14,680 --> 02:12:23,080
in, you know, the families of the victims of 9-11 are suing the Saudi government, trying to get

1038
02:12:24,120 --> 02:12:28,760
more information about the people that are involved in that. And Bayoumi is one of the

1039
02:12:28,760 --> 02:12:35,240
people that they have on their list of people to talk to. But Bayoumi is such a generous fellow

1040
02:12:35,240 --> 02:12:42,520
that he offers to help them find a housing in San Diego, where he has a place. And so he fronts

1041
02:12:42,520 --> 02:12:49,720
them some money. He sets them up in San Diego. Bayoumi and other people in his circle begin

1042
02:12:49,720 --> 02:12:58,120
receiving money from the wife of the Saudi ambassador in Washington, DC, ostensibly for

1043
02:12:58,120 --> 02:13:03,960
an operation for the wife or, you know, these, you know, but it's significant thousands and

