02:14:30,520 --> 02:14:40,440
satisfactorily accounted for. Another thing that's going on, you know, they arrived in January 15th,

1055
02:14:40,920 --> 02:14:50,760
and in March the CIA finds out that they're in the U.S. Probably, you know, Prince Turkey, you know,

