02:15:00,040 --> 02:15:10,120
about that. So that's probably where it came from. So in March, this is 21 months before 9-11,

1058
02:15:10,120 --> 02:15:16,680
almost two years. The CIA knows that Al Qaeda is in America. And this is at a time when they're,

1059
02:15:16,680 --> 02:15:20,680
they say their hair's on fire about, you know, about Al Qaeda, that we're under threat,

1060
02:15:20,680 --> 02:15:27,320
they're going to the White House. And yet they know that Al Qaeda is in San Diego. And moreover,

1061
02:15:27,880 --> 02:15:38,600
Midhar's wife is in Yemen. She comes from a very Al Qaeda, jihadi family. Her name is

1062
02:15:38,600 --> 02:15:48,920
Hoda Al Hada. And the Al Hada household, because it's such a hotspot, we've got wires on the phone.

1063
02:15:48,920 --> 02:15:52,040
We've got the phone. Yeah. So I think it's on-

