02:16:19,960 --> 02:16:27,640
Cuso and the other suspects, he asks specifically, well, he kind of, I think through that questioning

1069
02:16:27,640 --> 02:16:36,280
comes to learn of the meeting that took place in Malaysia. And asks explicitly on at least

1070
02:16:36,280 --> 02:16:45,720
three occasions for information from the CIA about these two guys in the US. And he is stonewalled.

1071
02:16:46,040 --> 02:16:53,160
It's not casual either. A request like that goes to the director of the FBI who sends

