02:23:50,600 --> 02:23:58,440
time has passed enough that I can say this. I wrote an article about Iman Elzawari for The

1130
02:23:58,440 --> 02:24:11,800
New Yorker and the CIA asked to talk to me. And so I was picked up by an FBI agent who worked at

1131
02:24:11,800 --> 02:24:17,960
the CIA and driven to CIA headquarters and gone up the seventh floor and there was a conference

1132
02:24:17,960 --> 02:24:31,080
room and I met with Alex Station. They were about 20 something people there. And the meeting started

