02:24:31,080 --> 02:24:38,040
off in Arabic. And I said, Kula hah dah hai na bakadam aarvi? You know, everybody here speaks

1134
02:24:38,040 --> 02:24:45,160
Arabic and they had learned it in the last couple of years. I was impressed by that. But I was not

1135
02:24:45,160 --> 02:24:50,040
